    "body": "Right now we are flushing the DB environment (https://docs.oracle.com/cd/E17276_01/html/api_reference/C/envclose.html) with `DBEnv->CloseDb(filename)`.\r\nIs there a reason why we wouldn't want to use `DB->Sync()` (https://docs.oracle.com/cd/E17276_01/html/api_reference/C/dbsync.html)?",
